author: Nostalgia Nerd
description:
A quick montage from the Retro Computer Festival; packed with rare machines; classic home computers; obscure prototypes; and hardware that defined entire eras of computing. From 8-bit icons to forgotten oddities; it’s a full hit of pure nostalgia in one short clip.

title: So. Many. Rare. Computers.
